title: Governance #4: First network vote
body:
PROPOSAL SUMMARY: After much deliberation, we have narrowed the substantial list of networks down to 3 chains for Thorus platform launch. 

READ MORE DESCRIPTION HERE:
https://medium.com/waultfinance/governance-4-first-network-vote-now-open-451ed253fef2

1) AVALANCHE – The Avalanche network has been very successful since its mainnet launch. AVAX has achieved a current TVL of over 20B while maintaining fast transaction speeds at a relatively low cost.

2) FANTOM – The Fantom network is another Defi powerhouse with a current TVL of 5.4B, according to Defilama, and growing. Onboarding/bridging is also a simple process, whether bridging or using centralized exchanges.

3) CRONOS – Cronos is a new EVM network created by Crypto.com. While Crypto.com has been around for some time, the network is only a few weeks old. However, in this short period, Cronos has achieved a TVL of 911M.

QUESTION: What first chain are you voting for?
author: 0x25932EfC092400f7bc62ecbb2C3EAB67F9e8bA55
